title: PetSmart Retail Locations, USA, 11.2008
name: PetSmart Retail Locations, USA, 11.2008
description:
This dataset locates all the PetSmart locations across the USA as of 11.26.2008. The data includes: Store name, Store Number, Address, City, State, Zip, Phone, and lat/lon location.
The data comes from the PetSmart website at petsmart.com. The lat/lons were obtained by running addresses through a geocoder at gpsvisualizer.com and then spotchecking the mapped locations for correctness.
